{"tid":936904,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"臭雞扮夠可憐未？","createTime":"2018-12-11T06:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T12:04:59.000Z","uid":10759,"like":37,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e40216e7cd28a9488032931e135ae9d00a065d73","tid":936904,"uid":10759,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T06:41:34.000Z","msg":"對住啲仔就講到自己有幾慘得咁慘<br />\n又講到自己與世無爭唔介意又剩<br />\n其實就自己係屋企嬲到dum哂地<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心寒？我見到你做啲嘢仲心寒啦<br />\n明明有個拍緊拖又唔係唔穩定嘅男朋友<br />\n你仲好意思可以周圍識異性同人pm同人單獨出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞完一個又一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲可以厚面皮到問啲仔點解唔同我flirt啊？？？我覺得玩吓無問題喎！！！<br />\n嘩 真係虧你講得出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有男朋友就唔該你檢點啲啦<br />\n咁啱你又搵到個易沉船又願意同你傾唔介意<br />\n人哋消失幾日你又係咁搵人驚死人哋真係唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過你都幾厲害 男朋友係正你隔離都可以同其他男仔pm<br />\n唔知你男朋友知道咗你對佢咁好唔知佢會點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffea9bc890173809942d6725298ebce3c570881","tid":936904,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T06:41:47.000Z","msg":"夠了"},{"pid":"3600a8a619a55d9182563b65cef221ac71ab6c75","tid":936904,"uid":93655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T06:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8935e4672b00688f6ba10d74ef9a7f1c9b2b0ebb","tid":936904,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T06:44:32.000Z","msg":"做唔到第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf89d148c66d29322d0ab9afb9176dd75b972fc4","tid":936904,"uid":10759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8935e4672b00688f6ba10d74ef9a7f1c9b2b0ebb","tid":936904,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":